#Algorithm Notes
#Gini(total) = 1 - (cuisine1/totalcount)^2 - ...

#Gini(ingredient:yes or no)(partition): yescount/partitiontotal ( 1 - (yescuisine1/yescount)^2 - (yescuisine2/yescount)^2)...) + nocount/partitiontotal ( 1 - (nocuisine1/nocount)^2...)
